item.title: Loading wikipedia on a 45 year old modem
item.dc:creator: @runescape3dude runescape3dude
item.description:

[quote=“Fat Cookies, post:6, topic:280847”][quote author=T4_ link=topic=370911.msg2802788#msg2802788 date=1243543558]

cause new ones get hot.
